# SmartClient runtime (external symlink, ~260MB)
extension/smartclient

# Plugin assembly outputs (extension/apps/<id>/) — private plugins are
# assembled from outside repos at build time and never enter public history.
# Checked-in exceptions:
#   - apps/README.md       — explains the convention
#   - apps/index.json      — plugin discovery list
#   - apps/hello-runtime/  — in-tree reference plugin
#   - apps/horsebread/PLAN.md (legacy placeholder)
extension/apps/*
!extension/apps/README.md
!extension/apps/index.json
!extension/apps/_loaded.js
!extension/apps/hello-runtime/
!extension/apps/horsebread/
extension/apps/horsebread/*
!extension/apps/horsebread/PLAN.md

# Screenshots & data files
Capture.PNG
twinspires-races.txt
*.png
nul
.specstory/
.npmrc
